title&#34;&gt;summary&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;Prepend&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;one&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;or&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;multiple&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;values&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;to&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;list&lt;/span&gt;(在列表前添加一个或多个值)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;since&lt;/span&gt;: 1.0.0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;LPUSHX&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;key&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;summary&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;Prepend&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;value&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;to&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;list&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;only&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;the&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;list&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;exists&lt;/span&gt;（仅当列表存在时，在列表前加上一个值）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;function&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;title&#34;&gt;since&lt;/span&gt;: 2.2.0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#3